---
import Layout from './layout.astro'
import { getAssetPrefix } from '../../../../utils/path.js'
---

<Layout
  title="Why Health Testing Matters for Breeding Cats"
  description="Learn how genetic and health screenings help ensure healthy, happy kittens and responsible breeding practices."
>
  <!-- Blog Post Content -->
  <section class="bg-body py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
          <!-- Blog Heading, Category, and Date -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span
              class="badge text-primary bg-primary-subtle fs-6 mb-2"
              data-aos="fade-down"
              data-aos-duration="1200">Health</span
            >
            <h1
              class="fw-semibold mb-2"
              data-aos="fade-down"
              data-aos-delay="200"
              data-aos-duration="1200"
            >
              Why Health Testing Matters for Breeding Cats
            </h1>
            <p class="text-muted" data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-delay="200" data-aos-duration="1200">
              <i class="ri-calendar-line me-1"></i>12 Jan 2025
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Cover Image -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <img
              src={getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/cat-theme/1/persian-1.jpg')}
              alt="Blog Cover"
              class="img-fluid rounded-5"
              style="max-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; width: 100%;"
              data-aos="fade-in"
              data-aos-duration="1200"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Blog Content -->
          <div class="mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1200">
            <p>
              Breeding cats is a serious responsibility that goes far beyond pairing two animals
              together. Ethical breeders are not only passionate about their chosen breed, but also
              deeply committed to the health and wellbeing of their cats—and the kittens they
              produce. One of the most important tools in responsible breeding is health testing.
            </p>
            <p>
              Health testing allows breeders to identify genetic conditions, infectious diseases,
              and other medical issues that may not be obvious in outwardly healthy cats.
            </p>
            <p>
              Skipping health testing may save time and money in the short term—but the consequences
              can be devastating. Breeding cats without testing can result in litters with
              preventable diseases, birth defects, or shortened lifespans. It also places emotional
              and financial burdens on kitten buyers who may not be prepared for the challenges of a
              chronically ill pet.
            </p>
            <p>
              Responsible breeders use health testing not just as a tool—but as a standard. It
              demonstrates integrity, respect for the breed, and compassion for the cats and
              families involved.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Share Button -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <button
              class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4"
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-duration="1200"
            >
              <i class="ri-share-line me-1"></i>Share this post
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- Author Section -->
          <div
            class="d-flex align-items-center border-top pt-4 mb-5"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1200"
          >
            <img
              src={getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/avatars/avatar1.jpg')}
              alt="Author Image"
              class="rounded-circle me-3"
              width="64"
              height="64"
            />
            <div>
              <h6 class="mb-1">
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-body">Jane Smith</a>
              </h6>

              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                Certified cat health advocate with 10+ years of experience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Similar Posts -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1200">Similar Posts</h4>
            <div class="row g-4">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div
                  class="card border rounded-5 h-100 p-0"
                  data-aos="flip-up"
                  data-aos-delay="100"
                  data-aos-duration="1200"
                >
                  <img
                    src={getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/cat-theme/1/persian-2.jpg')}
                    class="card-img-top rounded-top-5"
                    style="max-height: 200px; object-fit: cover;"
                    alt="Similar Post 1"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Catteries vs. Backyard Breeders</h5>
                    </a>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted mb-2">
                      Understand the difference between ethical catteries and irresponsible
                      breeding, and how to choose a reputable cat breeder.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="link-primary text-decoration-none">Read More</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div
                  class="card border rounded-5 h-100 p-0"
                  data-aos="flip-up"
                  data-aos-delay="200"
                  data-aos-duration="1200"
                >
                  <img
                    src={getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/cat-theme/1/persian-3.jpg')}
                    class="card-img-top rounded-top-5"
                    style="max-height: 200px; object-fit: cover;"
                    alt="Similar Post 2"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Real Cost of Raising Healthy Kittens</h5>
                    </a>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted mb-2">
                      Why kittens from responsible breeders cost more, and what goes into raising
                      well-socialized, healthy cats.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="link-primary text-decoration-none">Read More</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
